VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT Log\.[dviweVIWDE]\s*\(.*(?:password|token|secret|apiKey|credential|authToken|accessToken)
WHEN EXPR MISSING:BuildConfig\.DEBUG|if\s*\(\s*BuildConfig\.DEBUG|if\s*\(\s*DEBUG
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects Android log statements that reference sensitive data outside a debug build guard.
TRACE Externalized mobile rule logic for Sensitive Data Written to Android Logs.
